Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏·浦木少尉經歷了實戰的考驗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.50,0:00:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與搶奪GUNDAM2號機的男人進行了對決
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.75,0:00:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿納貝爾·卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.30,0:00:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾是震撼了聯邦的ZION的王牌機師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使指尖凍結
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喉嚨乾涸的戰慄感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及逐一逝去同伴的魂魄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對追擊的浦木不屑一顧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM2號機在晨霧中隱去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木的初戰充滿了屈辱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)\fs60}出擊阿爾比昂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿爾比昂的艦長席那普斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是宏·浦木少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對此次擅自使用1號機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不做辯解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型機如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動性及動力都是最強的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從賈布羅來的通信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到主監視器上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13號優先，以我的名義去…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了，大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾比昂的修復進度如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高雲中將
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概還要花七、八小時左右
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監視衛星方面怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒有新情報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的問題是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止他們逃往宇宙一事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會適得其反？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把奪去的核彈投向賈布羅？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮官必須時常考慮到最壞的事態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且也沒有立場能依賴於南極條約
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你們繼續核彈頭和新型MS的奪還作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加快阿爾比昂的修理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席那普斯艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭已結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一發仍可奪去幾千萬人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是絕不可使用的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2號槍膛的調整器還得進行最終設置…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了，少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒實現取回2號機的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1號機交還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就軍人來說很坦率呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告阿爾比昂全體乘員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦由現在起開始核彈以及新型2號機的奪還任務
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判明敵人的逃走路線後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就進入作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體人員準備起航
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，你是民間人士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以還是下船的好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍後再向公司本部請示
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在首要的是1號機的檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼垂頭喪氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊，宏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像會派增援MS和身經百戰的機師來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也打得很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的對手似乎是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年戰爭之時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為所羅門的惡夢的卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那樣的傢伙戰鬥還能生還就很了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被大尉救了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要去探望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這麼熱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可是冬天啊，真是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏可是南半球啊，中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍命難違啊，蒙夏兄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的休假竟被叫到這種地方來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可正在約會啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話聽過無數回了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗不會再等我了，畜生！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的小姐們！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣，今晚來陪我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個不吸取教訓的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs38\3c&H00ef877e}喂！你想幹什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他根本沒有學習機能吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊！那個那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那將會成為我的愛機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒決定是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的幾位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM現正維護中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請離開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就宛如一朵綻放的玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何貴幹？中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是貝爾納爾德·蒙夏中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日起調配於此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的芳名是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·巴普爾頓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是機師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來參觀1號機的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我眼中已只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙夏中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事就請你下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妨礙我工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這性格我喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我理想中的女性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個中尉是剛才騷擾我部下的色狼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你、你這大塊頭女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事的話就讓你嘗嘗苦頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰怕誰！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後將是共事的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識這個基地的巴寧格中尉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴寧格中尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說大尉的話，他正在醫療班的帳篷裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉出什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早負傷入院了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷勢真的不要緊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庸醫的小題大做而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:10:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這種…根本算不上傷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉，阿爾比昂獲得MS和機師的補給
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說不再需要我們了是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.85,0:10:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼不用我們作戰也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴寧格大尉！大尉！大尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才聽說你被害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們到地下太平間白跑了一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還沒死啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是不死身的第4小隊出身的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那麼容易死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是慰問禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補充人員就是你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被派來參加此次的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托他的福休假也飛掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是新機種就這麼輕易被奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且連1號機也追了上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然沒辦法奪回還讓他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:11:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是這裏的機師太笨拙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追擊2號機的是我的小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個隊長應該付上全責
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我隊裏的浦木少尉和吉斯少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆去整理阿連他們的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個還是新人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的軍官學校出身的少尉大人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說不定很有潛力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說昨天的對手可是所羅門的惡夢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所羅門的惡夢？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還活著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法相信啊，大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個乳臭未乾的小子竟和ZION的卡多交手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙恢復起來還真花時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木少尉進來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那時…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做得再好點的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了，少佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:14:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金巴萊德也一直恭候著少佐的佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:14:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}金巴萊德：被ZION佔據的非洲橄欖巖礦山\N以前出產工業用鑽石，後被ZION改建為秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到非洲還要多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約一星期左右
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到真會用到那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏，你來真的？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你志願參加奪還作戰到底想幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我就這樣袖手旁觀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法忍受！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就要特地讓自己置身於險境？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是少尉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和所羅門的惡夢交過手了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不配作對手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:15:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那個卡多都交過手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定只是偷偷摸摸躲在一旁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巴寧格大尉和妮娜小姐救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我獨自應戰的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的實力！浦木少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮、妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你駕駛1號機時的數據
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難想像你初次搭乘的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就將性能發揮了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給自己點信心，浦木少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你特地拿這個來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專程拿給你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛技術半吊子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追女人倒有一套
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西給他看了也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1號機的機師是我們三人之中的一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種新人機師想要駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連萬分之一的可能都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:16:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不用說是眼睜睜放跑了2號機的小鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太戲弄他了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹也是巴寧格大尉的寶貝徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使身手不值一哂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1號機和妮娜小姐由我來駕馭你大可放心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼還是回家去找媽媽給你襯尿布吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙夏中尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光憑推測就隨便評論對手的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像是個對自己技術有信心的機師！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起中尉來或許浦木少尉會更出色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就來試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和浦木少尉比試一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就推薦他做GUNDAM的機師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就永遠別在我們面前出現
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要試試！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我試一下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，決定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏，太勉強了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手可是身經百戰的機師啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯，機會只有這一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何我都要奪回2號機！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在妮娜小姐面前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打得你叫不出聲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是艦橋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是蒙夏中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現類似敵機影的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM也帶著去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規則很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:18:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先用顏料彈擊中對手機體的一方就算勝出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來發令開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時OK
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別驚慌，小心地加速
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再開快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠快了，大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動得太過頭的話傷口又要裂開了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再磨磨蹭蹭就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GM Custom量產型
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}GM Custom：型號RGM-79N，一年戰爭後聯邦以RGM-79C GM改\N為原型再設計得到的機體，是專為王牌機師開發的增強型GM
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有特長就是它的特長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:18:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會逃跑嗎？少尉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙夏！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子注意點！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然厲害，中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那新型機的動作相當靈活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜鳥！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！求之不得！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉的行動好像有點魯莽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才像他嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個來，少尉能撐到什麼地步更讓人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木少尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼機動性啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能輸！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負已定！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪、哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎、怎麼會？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然輸了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.40,0:21:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了！贏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:21:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從吉斯那聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.10,0:22:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是胡來！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大、大尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之你們先回基地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後的事交給我處理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.45,0:22:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁閉一星期
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，保重
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是一星期，明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.55,0:22:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼妮娜和歐比爾都想隨船同行吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.90,0:22:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會聯絡艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.65,0:22:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其餘的人請留在基地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.60,0:22:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，請小心行事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.75,0:22:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:22:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.25,0:23:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧，大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷勢已無大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的事非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.40,0:23:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的部下們我約束不了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.10,0:23:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在此和你商討一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.40,0:23:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想請你以中隊長的身份留在船上
